        <p>This week I have worked at RAPP. My task was to build this website, using SQL server and Visual Studio. I have used programming languages such as <strong>asp.net</strong>, <strong>C#</strong>, <strong>css</strong> and <strong>HTML</strong>.</p>
        
        
